author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall corner bead tips…I’m using Strait-Flex Original for this outside corner. I apply setting-type joint compound with my 3 inch knife and embed the corner. After some light sanding and two more coats, this will look perfect. Visit homerepairtutor.com for more written tutorials and videos 🔥#drywall #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
